longBusinessSummary: Ostrom Climate Solutions Inc. provides carbon management solutions in Canada, Europe, the United States, and internationally. It operates through Carbon Management and Innovation, Domestic Land Use, International Land Use, and Retail Offset Sales divisions. The company engages in the verified emission reduction units, as well as project development consulting services, and other environmental consulting services. It also provides climate advisory, clean technology and industrial innovation, and nature-based solutions. The company was formerly known as NatureBank Asset Management Inc. and changed its name to Ostrom Climate Solutions Inc. in December 2021. Ostrom Climate Solutions Inc. was incorporated in 2005 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
